{
  "id": "adv_group_mna_01_04",
  "title": "長瀬麻奈 01 04",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（こうして麻奈と俺は、学業と芸能活動を）\n（二人三脚で続けていった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Just like this Mana and I continued our studies）\n（and entertainment activities together.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 5.966666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（知らないことばかりで、とても大変だったが）\n（同時に新鮮な体験でもあった。そして十ヶ月後）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（It was tough‚ filled with unfamiliar things‚）\n（but at the same time it’s a fresh experience. And ten months later…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.166666666666667,
      "endTime": 13.766666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_way_evening",
      "startTime": 15.016666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "デビューの日が決まったぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The date of your debut is confirmed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.066666666666666,
      "endTime": 17.633333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "麻奈、{user}",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mana‚ {user}.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.633333333333333,
      "endTime": 18.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04-mna001.m4a",
      "text": "……デビュー……\n…………え？　私？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Debut…\nWho? Me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.7,
      "endTime": 23.463991165161133,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "おめでとう！　良かったね！\n麻奈ちゃん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Congratulations! That’s great news!\nMana!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.666666666666668,
      "endTime": 26.508367268244427,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "随分、急に決まるものなんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was decided on all of a sudden.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.7,
      "endTime": 29.270249366760254,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "アイドルのデビューはいろいろな要素が重なって決まる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "An idol’s debut is decided based on various factors.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.466666666666665,
      "endTime": 34.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "実力、周囲の状況――最適なタイミングを計っていた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ability‚ circumstances――I was waiting for the best timing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.2,
      "endTime": 39.766666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04-mna002.m4a",
      "text": "いつ、どこで歌わせてもらえるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When and where do I get to sing?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.96666666666667,
      "endTime": 43.31387759844462,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "来月、星見公園の野外ステージで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your debut concert will be next month",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.5,
      "endTime": 47.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "デビューライブだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "at the outdoor stage in Hoshimi Park.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.46666666666667,
      "endTime": 48.766666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "私も応援に行くよ！　絶対盛り上げようね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll go to cheer you on! Hopefully it goes well!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.96666666666667,
      "endTime": 52.4767573038737,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04-mna003.m4a",
      "text": "うん、遙子ちゃん\n嬉しいよ。ありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks Haruko-chan.\nThat means a lot to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.666666666666664,
      "endTime": 58.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（麻奈……？　ちっとも嬉しそうじゃないけど）\n（どうしたんだ……？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Mana… She doesn’t look happy at all.）\n（I wonder what’s the matter.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.333333333333336,
      "endTime": 63.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_coast-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_living_noon",
      "startTime": 64.75
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "なあ、何が不満なんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ what's bothering you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.8,
      "endTime": 68.18718824386596,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04-mna004.m4a",
      "text": "…………\nどうして、分かったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…………\nHow did you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.4,
      "endTime": 72.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "一応、麻奈のマネージャーだからな\nバイトでアシスタントだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I am your manager‚ after all.\nJust an assistant on a part-time job.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.4,
      "endTime": 76.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04-mna005.m4a",
      "text": "さすがだね、{user}くん\n私のこと、よく見ててくれてるんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Impressive‚ {user}‚\nyou really pay attention to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.16666666666667,
      "endTime": 82.84666678110759,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "話してくれよ、何が不満なんだ？\n麻奈の目指してたステージに立てるんだぞ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on‚ tell me‚ what's bothering you?\nWe're working towards your dream stage‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.03333333333333,
      "endTime": 89,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04-mna006.m4a",
      "text": "{user}くん、誤解しないで\nデビューはゴールじゃなくてスタートなの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}‚ don't get me wrong.\nDebut isn't the finish line. It's the start.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.2,
      "endTime": 93.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04-mna007.m4a",
      "text": "私も調べてみたの。今はね\n毎年五百組近いアイドルがデビューしてるんだって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I did some research. Recently‚\nnearly five hundred idol groups debuts every year.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94,
      "endTime": 100.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04-mna008.m4a",
      "text": "でも、そのほとんどが\nデビューしただけで、消えちゃう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But most of them‚\nthey disappear after their debut.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.1,
      "endTime": 105.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04-mna009.m4a",
      "text": "私は、沢山歌いたい\nデビューしてすぐ消えたくなんてない！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to sing for a long time.\nI don't want to vanish right after my debut!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.46666666666667,
      "endTime": 111.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mana…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.5,
      "endTime": 112.46000002622604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（俺はデビューさえ出来れば）\n（プロにさえなればいい、と思っていた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（As long as I make a debut‚ as long as I can become a pro‚）\n（I thought that's all that matters.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.66666666666667,
      "endTime": 118.16666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈の気持ちは分かったよ。俺も覚悟を決めた\nデビューまで、出来る限りのことをしよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand how you feel‚ Mana.\nUntil our debut‚ let's do everything we can.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.36666666666666,
      "endTime": 126.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04-mna010.m4a",
      "text": "うん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.23333333333333,
      "endTime": 126.9675283451875,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "長瀬麻奈の歌を\n少しでも沢山の人に届けるために",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To reach as many people as possible\nwith your songs.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.16666666666667,
      "endTime": 131.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04-mna011.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう。頼りにしてるね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you. I'm counting on you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.8,
      "endTime": 134.84473911921185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistaion-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.01666666666668
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistaion-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.01666666666668
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_04-mna012.m4a",
      "text": "私、長瀬麻奈のデビューライブ、来週の日曜日\n星見公園の野外ステージで行います！",
